    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro <expan><abbr>sal</abbr><ex>ute</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> C<lb break="no" n="2"/><expan><abbr>aes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Tra</abbr><ex>iani</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Hadri</abbr><ex>ani</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>porta</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>muru</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> per <lb n="4"/>pedes <expan><abbr>lon</abbr><ex>gum</ex></expan> C <expan><abbr>altu</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> VII <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>iuvent</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>colen</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iove</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> Doli<lb break="no" n="6"/><expan><abbr>chen</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> inpe<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>sa</abbr></expan> sua <expan><abbr>fec</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Zeile 2: TR-, DR-, AV- Ligatur; Zeile 3: TA-, ET-, PE-Ligatur; Zeile 4: DE-, LT-Ligatur; Zeile 5: VE-, NT-, LE-, VE-Ligatur; D und O verschränkt; Zeile 6: HE-Ligatur. Datierung: Führung des Titels &amp;apos;pater patriae&amp;apos; durch Hadrian offiziell seit 128, jedoch auch früher auf Inschriften und Münzen zu finden, daher unsicherer t.p.q. Sekundär verwendet als Baumaterial in der Umfassungsmauer auf dem Ringwall des Pfaffenberges. (B): AE 1936: Z. 2: Hadr(iani).</p>
            </div>
